Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 这里是冲仓家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 啊 那个 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一个学校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 冲仓同学 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想…看到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 你现在就想看到未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 现在就想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总之我们见面说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去透子家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来我家的话你回去会很晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 这太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把事情做完就去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之后会有一位非常重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作品 对 我要做作品了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以不要进工房哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是要在吃饭前做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子真有热情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪喜欢的不是小柳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓同学要来我家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪和小柳都是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这一点从前以后都不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 就算我的心意不变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们之间的关系  也可能发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳…在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把小柳弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到未来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子的媒介是玻璃的原因就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来客人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我正忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐一直受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}马上给您泡茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用了 冲仓同学马上就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要对爸爸妈妈保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说是今天吃炸猪排哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}麻烦你过来 我倒像是要赶你回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是想看看小柳和小雪的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被井美雪哉告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为…为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳注意到小雪有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来找我谈心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}估计没注意到的只有你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子看了他们的未来之后准备怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想找到不让他们分开的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}先不说能不能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做什么事都很拼命是你的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天大家会一起去爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓同学也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想你刚来这里 是不是朋友还不怎么多…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我喜欢一个人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没注意到的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.10,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在还赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.72,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 有点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是也没有其他方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.85,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}无论怎么想都会觉得这个很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以啊 我不是说了女孩子是需要这个的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么爬山需要吹风机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是头发乱了该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说起来山上是没有电的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}当然是充电式的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等你们好久了 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早～上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好 开始爬山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太慢了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}走错了一条路 啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的 真的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相信我这个关心弟弟的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是觉得危险的话 马上给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.14,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 集合地点见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家 快退后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我呢 感觉见过小幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 可以叫你小幸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说到医院 这里的人都是去那家综合医院的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 那条挂链好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在哪里买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是别人送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 真有品味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么人 恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 是我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哎呀 那家伙很行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我家的那位不懂女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又很介意个子矮这种无所谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是内心还是很善良的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要和他好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太期待今天 结果昨天没睡着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天冲仓同学来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓同学就是那个转学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看起来像是喜欢山的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是邀请他也来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我邀请他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是他说喜欢一个人爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「孤高之人」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我更喜欢和大家一起爬山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还有三十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢 坐车子很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然没有坐过过山车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我想感觉也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}过山…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么 到时候我会来接她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 多谢 姐姐也多小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来去如风的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在家里就成台风了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快看 是山哦 山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那边是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}刚才爬的就是山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心情真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 那边的山还有积雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那里是日乃出山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我该做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}用这个打些水来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪里能打到水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 你是最拿不了重东西的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉当然是负责搭帐篷的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也不用那么费劲地找河流啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其实附近就有个接水的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有些话想问透子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 找到小溪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哇 好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要和雪交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你在干什么呢 真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这里铺好了座位 可以看书哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去找那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她们确实太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是不知道在哪里接水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其实旁边就有条水管的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那家伙大概也是个爱操心的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜欢炒面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我喜欢多加些红姜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这里就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}让我大胆行动的是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过 我选的时间也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你是怎么看雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说实话 吓了一跳什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白之后一般不会说「多谢」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我说过这句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}话说 为什么你会知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你会和雪交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不会交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然小雪很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我的恋爱感应器没有发动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子身上好像没有装备这种东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没能让你看到真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你们不会交往的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是透子喜欢雪的话 就更容易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我已经决定要支援你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我 不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想迷路都迷不了的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}惨叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快给老娘滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}顺便 给老娘接一辈子水去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你那…一直…热心…读书的身影是如此迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在我眼中…宛若人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是诗什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 要放面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}烫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}水…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪里要用水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}祐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}醍醐灌顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}灌你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的着急了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.12,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吧 好好品味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}友情的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.64,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你手艺还挺不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.57,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一般般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.01,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得真的很厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:01.12,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你夸得这么直接感觉真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.52,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}别说恶心恶心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.60,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想把这个加到风道的菜单里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.64,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这想法不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.14,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是被采用了我一定会去吃的 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.24,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在我眼中 你就像人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我终于察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}手 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没有烫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作为悉心照顾我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不… 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在就可以看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…喜欢「幸」这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我觉得必须要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有比我更适合小雪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为小雪是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没关系的 来 先上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对了 我来的路上看到野猪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:45.30,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相当凶暴的 碰到的话装睡可行不通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.08,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不是熊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.42,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 是这样来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 没帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很快就收拾好了 没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回去的时候是直接送到家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:01.11,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哦 到底是有了动机 麻利多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 下次就在咖啡店见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.29,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.63,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没～什～么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 今天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.94,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}别再用这种奇怪的说法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.90,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没～什～么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 真的要多小点心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:19.42,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好 没问题 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.39,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 身体不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那么 在碰到野猪之前下山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}下山比上山更容易发生事故呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白了 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.79,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一直到家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 下山我走前面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}紧紧跟着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}致透子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天真的多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我会再联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}阳菜啊 要是被好朋友喜欢的人告白了 该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没什么怎么办的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对告白的人只有喜欢不喜欢这两个回答喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不愧是阳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是 昨天那个哥哥没有一起去登山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没有啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱真是个奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳 是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉有些帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你喜欢那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是不是有点装模作样？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================TITLE====================
